Template-Plugin-POSIX version 0.01
==================================

This is a plugin for Perl Template Toolkit. It imports almost all the
POSIX functions to the Template representation language, leading
this mini-language to a really serious programming language.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Template

The test suite requires the following modules:

  Test::More
  File::Compare

